{
  "texts": [
    "Previous studies have shown that two formants (N = 2) are enough for intelligible reconstruction 51, but we use N = 6 for more accurate synthesis in our experiments.",
    "Unvoice filters.",
    "We construct the unvoice filter by adding a single broadband filter F t û (f) to the formant filters for each time step t. The broadband filter F t û (f) has the same form as equation (1) but has its own learned prototype filter G û (f).",
    "The speech parameters corresponding to the broadband filter include (α t û, f t û, b t û).",
    "We do not impose a relationship between the centre frequency f t û and the bandwidth b t û."
  ]
}